%h2.main.upcoming Tea times
- if !current_user.future_attendances.count.zero?
  %ul.upcoming
    - current_user.future_attendances.each do |a|
      %li.tea-time= render partial: 'teatime_info', locals: {tea_time: a.tea_time, att: a, without_button: true}
- else
  %p 
    You're not scheduled for any tea times! Let's change that.
    =link_to "Go schedule a tea time!", schedule_city_path(current_user.home_city)
